title: Purchasing 2 or 3 rare meridians from Art Blocks for 50-75 eth
body:
Hi all,

Last week Art Blocks ran a wonderful mint called meridians from Matt Deslauriers. 

https://opensea.io/collection/art-blocks-playground?search[sortAscending]=true&search[sortBy]=PRICE&search[stringTraits][0][name]=Meridian&search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=All%20Meridians

This one is getting very positive reviews and is seen by many insiders and people on discord as a possible top 5 classic from Art Block (similar to fidenza). The prices have gone up quite a bit but there are definitely still some opportunities.  Goal is to buy 2 or 3 rare and beautiful pieces.  I think with a budget of 50-75 eth we will get there. We are not going to regret this.
